## üéµ GENRE SUGGESTIONS

### **Component 3 Genres** (Listening Analysis)
Best for genres with:
- Clear production features
- Era-specific techniques
- Identifiable effects
- Historical context

**Recommended:**
- Funk (1970s-1980s)
- Disco (1970s)
- Synthwave (1980s)
- Britpop (1990s)
- Grunge (1990s)
- Soul/R&B (1960s-1970s)
- Post-Punk (1970s-1980s)
- New Wave (1980s)

