- Trap (2010s)
- Lo-Fi Hip-Hop (2010s-2020s)
- Dubstep (2000s-2010s)
- Drum & Bass (1990s-2000s)
- Future Bass (2010s)
- Techno (1980s-present)
- UK Garage (1990s-2000s)

