## üìä COMPARISON CHART

| Feature | Component 3 | Component 4 |
|---------|-------------|-------------|
| **Focus** | Listening & Analysis | Production Knowledge |
| **Total Marks** | 75 | 60 |
| **Time** | 90 minutes | 60 minutes |
| **Section A** | 40 marks (4√ó10) | 30 marks (10 short) |
| **Section B** | 35 marks (15+20) | 30 marks (3√ó10) |
| **Question Types** | 14 types | 4 main types |
| **Requires** | Audio tracks | Technical knowledge |
| **Tests** | Listening skills | Production skills |
| **Output** | Exam + mark scheme + track list | Quiz + mark scheme + reference guide |

